            <title>實試 Sony FE 50-150mm F2 GM  人像半身 Close Up 至全身一支鏡頭完全覆蓋</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 14:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機測試]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304556</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 今日正式發佈全新鏡頭 FE 50-150mm F2 GM，屬於全球首款具備恆定 F2.0 大光圈的中遠攝變焦鏡頭 ，屬於 G Master 系列最新旗艦之作。我們 unwire 記者早前就到了發佈會會場，親自試用這支極具份量的大光圈新鏡頭。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304557" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609-694x508.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="508" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609-694x508.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304558" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC04297" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468849118/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468849118_74336c18d8_b.jpg" alt="DSC04297" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04259" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468848073/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468848073_a1cf7c9114_b.jpg" alt="DSC04259" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>點擊<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/albums/72177720325319072/">此連結</a>看今次試相</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-694x541.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="541" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-694x541.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-scaled.jpg 1154w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>全球首款 50-150mm F2 恆定光圈變焦鏡頭</h2><p>Sony FE 50-150mm F2 GM 是首支橫跨 50mm 至 150mm 焦段、並具備恆定 F2 光圈的遠攝變焦鏡頭，專為新世代影像創作者設計，涵蓋人像、婚禮、體育等多樣拍攝場景。無論在 50mm 廣角端拍攝婚禮場景，還是在 150mm 端捕捉運動瞬間，都可呈現細膩清晰的主體與柔和自然的散景。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626-528x580.jpg" alt="" width="528" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626-528x580.jpg 528w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626.jpg 819w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 528px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC04285" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468782784/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468782784_1d831726f6_b.jpg" alt="DSC04285" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04351" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940820/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940820_6fc7222633_b.jpg" alt="DSC04351" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04323" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468848633/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468848633_3e1779189c_b.jpg" alt="DSC04323" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04360" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54467748612/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54467748612_19a051b313_b.jpg" alt="DSC04360" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>光學設計與解析力表現</h2><p>鏡頭採用 17 組 19 片光學結構，包含 2 片 XA 極致非球面鏡片、2 片非球面鏡片、2 片 Super ED 超低色散鏡片，以及 3 片 ED 低色散鏡片，強效抑制色差，提升畫質。加上 Sony 獨家 Nano AR 納米鍍膜 II，能有效減少炫光和鬼影，即使在強烈逆光環境下也能保有清晰對比。</p><p>根據 Sony 內部測試，這支鏡頭在最大光圈 F2 下，無論是 50mm 還是 150mm，從畫面中央到邊緣都維持極高解像度與對比度，媲美定焦鏡的光學品質。</p><p><a title="DSC04269" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54467749442/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54467749442_d373d9c7c2_b.jpg" alt="DSC04269" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>散景效果柔和自然</h2><p>FE 50-150mm F2 GM 配備 11 片圓形光圈葉片，營造順滑柔和的背景虛化效果，減少洋蔥圈紋理，呈現乾淨細膩的散景，完美襯託主體。無論是人像的眼神交流，或是動作瞬間，都賦予影像更好的層次感。</p><p><a title="DSC04450" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940085/in/album-72177720325319072" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940085_b5a18fb692_b.jpg" alt="DSC04450" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04408" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468587276/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468587276_fe59d8772b_b.jpg" alt="DSC04408" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04262" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940270/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940270_c3d3e86210_b.jpg" alt="DSC04262" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04445" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468783054/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468783054_680d6b7f09_b.jpg" alt="DSC04445" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04410" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468941120/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468941120_64b44397c1_b.jpg" alt="DSC04410" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>靈活穩定的手持拍攝體驗</h2><p>鏡頭採用內變焦設計，長時間拍攝時，無需擔心鏡頭重心改變影響平衡感。整體尺寸為 102.8mm × 200mm，重量約 1340 克（不含腳架座），適合各類手持拍攝場合。相比同為遠攝變焦的 FE 70-200mm F2.8 GM OSS II，FE 50-150mm F2 GM 提供更大光圈與更靈活的焦段選擇。雖然鏡身足有 1340 克，但對於日常工作例如婚攝工作者來説，這支鏡頭可在不同焦段都有 F2 光圈，靈活拍攝之餘也能獲得極為柔和散景，只要工作能順利完成，這支鏡頭的重量實在並非太大負擔。</p><h2>對焦性能卓越，捕捉精彩瞬間</h2><p>鏡頭搭載 4 組 XD 線性馬達，配合浮動對焦結構，FE 50-150mm F2 GM 實現高效靜音對焦，迅速鎖定快速移動的主體，無論是運動賽事還是野生動物皆能輕鬆掌握。特別是在搭配 α9 III 機身時，可發揮高達 120 fps 連拍性能，完美捕捉每一瞬間。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC04372" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468782084/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468782084_4c90ab4211_b.jpg" alt="DSC04372" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04366" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940495/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940495_151bf6d3de_b.jpg" alt="DSC04366" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04416" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468941360/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468941360_1df5d934f8_b.jpg" alt="DSC04416" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04326" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468849028/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468849028_f4c854cb3b_b.jpg" alt="DSC04326" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>影片拍攝特化設計</h2><p>為影片創作者而設，FE 50-150mm F2 GM 內建多項針對影片拍攝增強功能。鏡頭設計有效抑制呼吸效應，實現自然流暢的焦點轉移，配合 Alpha 機身的呼吸補償，拍攝時更顯細膩。內變焦與平衡設計，便於安裝於穩定器（gimbal），提升動態拍攝靈活性。</p><h2>操控性與細節設計</h2><p>鏡頭配置專業級操控按鈕與環節，包括三個可自訂對焦固定按鈕、全時 DMF 切換、光圈環與無段式光圈切換、變焦環及對焦環，提供靈活直觀操作。全新設計的遮光罩支援濾鏡轉接，腳架座亦可快速拆卸，符合專業使用需求。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625-694x430.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="430" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625-694x430.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">與 FE 28-70mm F2 GM （圖上左方）比較</p><h2>定價與上市資訊</h2><p>FE 50-150mm F2 GM 建議售價為 HKD 27,990，預售日期自 4 月 23 日至 4 月 27 日，透過 Sony Online Store、專門店及特約零售商進行預購，預計 4 月 29 日起正式取貨。預售期間加送 G 系列 TOUGH 規格 SD 卡（SF-G128T），價值 HKD 1,640。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm/dc/">實試 Sony FE 50-150mm F2 GM  人像半身 Close Up 至全身一支鏡頭完全覆蓋</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
