            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以往 iOS 要將錄音變成文字稿的話，需下載第三方應用程式，而程式質素良莠不齊，部分免費程式設有限額，收費程式價格普遍昂貴，而且部分用戶也許會擔心資訊安全問題。今日小編想和大家分享 iOS 內置的語音備忘錄轉文字稿功能，可以將錄音快速變成文字，而且不用擔心資料外洩。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ga-535x580.png" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ga-535x580.png 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ga.png 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲錄音一鍵變文字稿，支援廣東話！</p><h2>需求</h2><p>iPhone 12 或更新機款</p><p>iOS 18.4 或更新版本</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0435-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0435-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0435.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更新 iOS 18.4 後首次開啟原生「錄音機」會看見上面畫面，顯示可使用「轉寫紀錄」功能</p><h2>Step 1 開啟內置「錄音機」</h2><p>要使用錄音轉文字功能，首先你要開啟內置「錄音機」App，然後開始錄音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_1739-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_1739-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_1739.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開啟錄音機</p><p>現在你可以點擊紅色鍵錄音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8019-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8019-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8019.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲然後開始錄音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8020-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8020-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8020.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲錄完音就可以點擊停止鍵</p><br /><b>
